WEBVTT

00:12.050 --> 00:15.370
[1995]

00:13.000 --> 00:14.200
Ayo, Pak, lewat sini.

00:14.830 --> 00:16.290
Hujannya sudah agak reda.

00:16.520 --> 00:17.520
Cepat pindahkan.

00:17.580 --> 00:21.690
[Jiang Hansheng semasa kecil]

00:17.780 --> 00:19.260
Kalau tidak, nanti hujannya deras lagi.

00:19.260 --> 00:19.780
Ayo.

00:20.060 --> 00:20.720
Belok kiri.

00:21.240 --> 00:22.100
Hati-hati ya.

00:22.350 --> 00:23.870
Belok kanan.

00:24.480 --> 00:25.740
Aku mau main sebentar.

00:25.760 --> 00:27.360
Jalannya licin, hati-hati.

00:27.960 --> 00:29.020
Kalian lihat.

00:29.040 --> 00:30.110
Ada tetangga baru.

00:31.840 --> 00:32.180
Untukmu.

00:32.180 --> 00:33.200
Xiao Wu, cepat lari.

00:33.200 --> 00:33.960
Ayo!

00:35.080 --> 00:35.890
Giliranku!

00:35.920 --> 00:38.010
Jiang Cheng, kamu tidak
boleh bermain seperti ini.

00:38.010 --> 00:39.560
Adik kecil, siapa namamu?

00:39.960 --> 00:41.110
Namaku Zhou Jin.

00:42.790 --> 00:43.400
Hansheng.

00:44.270 --> 00:46.920
Lihat anak perempuan itu
larinya cepat sekali.

00:46.920 --> 00:48.590
Kakinya berputar seperti roda api.

00:48.590 --> 00:49.350
Tidak adil.

00:49.520 --> 00:50.470
Tidak adil.

00:50.470 --> 00:51.860
Tidak apa-apa, Yan Bin,
aku bantu kamu merebutnya.

00:51.860 --> 00:53.260
Kalau berani, ayo rebut.

00:55.660 --> 00:56.260
Hansheng.

00:57.070 --> 00:58.360
Lihat, di sini bagus sekali.

00:58.030 --> 01:02.130
[Jiang Bozhi, Ayah Jiang Hansheng]

00:58.840 --> 00:59.440
Iya, 'kan?

00:59.840 --> 01:00.610
Kelak,

01:00.630 --> 01:03.100
