01:17.890 --> 01:22.000
[Zhou Jin semasa kecil]

02:53.860 --> 02:59.829
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:00.190 --> 03:02.540
[Episode 2]

03:23.440 --> 03:24.440
