04:05.000 --> 04:05.670
Halo.

04:07.950 --> 04:08.390
Halo.

04:08.440 --> 04:11.640
Tim Investigasi Kriminal
Kepolisian Distrik Nancheng.

04:12.440 --> 04:13.070
